{"subject":"Chemistry","year":2011,"question":"Benzene has the formula:","options":["C₆H₆","C₆H₁₂","C₆H₁₀","C₆H₅"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Benzene is C₆H₆ (aromatic)."},
