{"subject":"Chemistry","year":2013,"question":"Aldehydes have the general formula R‑CHO. The functional group is:","options":["-CHO","-COOH","-OH","-CO-"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Aldehydes have the carbonyl group at the end of the chain (-CHO)."},
