{"subject":"Chemistry","year":2021,"question":"The IUPAC name for CH₃COCH₃ is:","options":["Propanone","Acetone","Propanal","Propanol"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"CH₃COCH₃ = propanone (acetone)."},
